In this folder:

quotes_stream.js: Using Cradle, interfaces with the CouchDB _changes stream for the quotes database, so 
                  that updates to the database are output by quotes_stream.js as they occur. 

quotes.js: Copied from previous recipe, 20-Retrieving Data from CouchDB with Cradle, modified for providing
           authorization details to CouchDB (if neccessary). Using Cradle, creates and connects to a CouchDB
           database (called quotes), and provides a command line interface for inserting quotes, and for finding
           quotes by author
          
